Hello! To create bold text in HTML, you can use the <b> tag to indicate bold text. Here’s an example:

<p><b>This text is bold.</b></p>

To style the bold text further, you can use CSS to change the font, size, and color. Here’s an example of how to use CSS to style bold text:

<style>

p {

font-size: 16px;

color: #0000ff;

}

</style>

